No. 64,

Misc.

Yancy v. United States. Seymour B¡. Goldman for petitioner. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Anderson, Robert S. Erdahl and J. F. Bishop for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit granted.

Mr. Justice Stewart took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.
